Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come watch, it's time for the appearance{\i0}\N{\i1}of the three leaves! (yay){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:18.85,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Three Leaves, Three Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning! I'll have three bowls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Did you eat, eat, eat, eat up your{\i0}\N{\i1}feminine charm along with your food?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, wait, wait a minute! I'm bad at P.E....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(I heard something good--{\i0}\N{\i1}I've found her weakness... Sorry){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I really want is to have fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my f-r-i-e-n-d-s!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try talking about silly things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like our love lives and other stuff like that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have any friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"My, you are direct!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're arrogant{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And high-handed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...etc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You have no reservations, do you?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:01:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are the three leaves running wild?!{\i0}\N{\i1}No one can stop them!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Nishiyama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Hayama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama is moved to tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Were those flashes of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.65,Main,,0,0,0,,She is still alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Ready, set!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, I, my, ambiguous me! (Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind's asleep... (zzz...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel refreshed! Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the three of us (fever!){\i0}\N{\i1}we have transcendent wisdom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when we're actually together, it's just noisy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(One more time!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look! Going my way forcefully forward! (Go! Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward! Yeah, going my way up! (Jump! Jump!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full speed ahead!{\i0}\N{\i1}Thanks for your hard work{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the story of my (wow!){\i0}\N{\i1}kind of strange and unusual{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Best and strongest life in history{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave her alone or Satan will burst out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure this is a high school girl's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}School life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cat Café"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"Tricky Cat"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:59.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, now, no fighting. Let's all be fwiends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, your drink's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Kono's gotten so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,She's quite the troublemaker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome! Is a counter seat okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:30.86,Main,,0,0,0,,"You've Got Them Hooked"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you awake? Let's go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"Central Shopping Arcade"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,"Central Shopping Arcade"\NI found a shop that you might like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"Central Shopping Arcade"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, like a boutique?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right here. I heard it's new. Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cat Café" "Tricky Cat"\NOh, right here. I heard it's new. Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No. I'd be cheating on Bel! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You've already been going to other places!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Tricky Cat Coupon" "30 min 600 yen→ 300 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"Tricky Cat Coupon" "30 min 600 yen→ 300 yen"\NHere's a coupon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}were {\i0}planning on coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:22.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I've heard about this place. I wish you'd\Ntold me we were coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,--My phone camera's not that great.\N--Welcome. Is a counter seat okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,--Sorry.\N--Welcome. Is a counter seat okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Nishiyama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Hayama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Just my luck. She'll ruin\Nmy cat café experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't this your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hello. Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Nishiyama. She's just a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were the one who took in\Nthe last of the cats Teru picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh. What did you name her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I never asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ours is "Bel" after "Beelzebub,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,because she was swarming with flies when we took her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"Bel"\Nbecause she was swarming with flies when we took her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I gave her a name that will give her a long life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"Eternal"\N"Eternal" or "El" for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Eternal"\N"El"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing. Eternal? It's just\Nobvious that you used the dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,the names of the kitties here are "Princess Konohana Sakuya,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,"Princess Konohana Sakuya"\Nthe names of the kitties here are "Princess Konohana Sakuya,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,the names of the kitties here are "Princess Konohana Sakuya,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lakshmi," "Viracocha," and "Teutates."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a little much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,All of their names are so refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, think about it. You'd be using\Nthose names at the vet or out in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Anyway, I didn't come here to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:05:00.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Mi? I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nishiyama, thanks for always coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello! Mi is here today. I was worried\Nsince she wasn't here last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.14,Main,,0,0,0,,--Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,--What a pro. You can tell she's a regular.\N--Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.52,Main,,0,0,0,,--What a pro. You can tell she's a regular.\N--She wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:20.32,Main,,0,0,0,,--Not like I care! I'm not angry at all!\N--She wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? I didn't know\NNishiyama goes to cat cafés.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It sounds like something she would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she'll send those pictures to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,If you just went to the cat café,\Nmaybe you don't need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't need what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A ticket for the petting zoo, Animal Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! I need that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"Animal Town" "Free Entrance"\NI got them from Sakura's mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.93,Main,,0,0,0,,and I thought you'd want it more than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, thanks! It's good for two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.27,Main,,0,0,0,,When should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's good until Sunday. We have three people,\Nso we can split the last ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,--I'm not going.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't really like animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.16,Main,,0,0,0,,And I have work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can go with your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,With my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:20.55,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow. So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Be gentler with the small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.47,Main,,0,0,0,,--That one is cute. But, this one is cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,--Calm down. Adore them one at a time! Big Sis!\N--That one is cute. But, this one is cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,--Calm down. Adore them one at a time! Big Sis!\N--That one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like it'd be tiring, and I\Nwouldn't have the time to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Animal Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,"Animal Town" "Free Entrance"\NAnimal Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"Animal Town" "Free Entrance"\NYup, Miss Yoko and I can't go. How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, Miss Yoko and I can't go. How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--What, really?!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you inviting Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:07:00.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think she'd like it?\NYou went to the cat café together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"Animal Town"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:22.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't think Nishiyama was going\Nto come because of Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Her love of animals was stronger, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo! You were worried, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know how they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,They went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,"Animal Town"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:42.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Welcome"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,They're still at the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:04.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're in charge of sales.\NAre you always working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,When will they go in?\NIt's been ten minutes already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, you'll run out\Nof memory at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't want to stay with Hayama.\NWe can split up or something from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,First, I'll go see the small animals that are closest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"Small Animal House"\Nthen go to the dog show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Dog Run" "Dog Show"\Nthen go to the dog show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, to the cat room, small dog petting corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.64,Main,,0,0,0,,"Doggie Petting House"\NThen, to the cat room, small dog petting corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.64,Main,,0,0,0,,watch the animal show, then the horse park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,"Horse Park"\Nwatch the animal show, then the horse park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:39.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Hayama. We can split up from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,No way. Did she have the same plan in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Jump and catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.82,Main,,0,0,0,,"Animal Town Doggie Show"\NJump and catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Jack succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama is moved to tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Despite the increasing number of unruly\Nhuman children, dogs are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, dogs are better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't think about it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess they're going around together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Will they be okay? They might\Nfight or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think Hayama will get angry today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She vowed to exercise self-discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Self-discipline?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,To broaden her experiences by\Ngetting to know all kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Freedom from worldly attachments or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:44.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if Nishiyama keeps\Npicking a fight with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.79,Main,,0,0,0,,There! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, Nishiyama. You've got them hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:57.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, it's natural if you own a cat.\NMaybe you're just not good at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not that good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you drinking juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:09.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm being healthy and got tea.\NCold juices have too much sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You're good. I should follow your example.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"Doggie Petting House"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,"Doggie Petting House"\NThat's a Weimaraner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a Weimaraner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:23.96,Main,,0,0,0,,In America, it's known as the "Grey Ghost."\NYou don't even know {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You sure know a lot\Nabout animals. You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm, I don't know why, but she's\Nin a good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like she's another person entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:40.14,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Nishiyama's going at full throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The dam might break soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Today was more fun than expected.\NI guess I could thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That Hayama! I was nice enough\Nto go with her and she... she--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you cheer me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, El.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,How was Animal Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It was fun! I want to go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:47.16,Main,,0,0,0,,And Nishiyama? How was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Same as usual. She got angry\Nhalf way and left, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The petting houses and shows were fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:12:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she left because I said that her getting\Ncarried away with herself was the funniest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Those two just don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"\NBut you know, I really thought it was a good chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,But you know, I really thought it was a good chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.40,Main,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:21.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You know how Hayama and Nishiyama\Nwent to Animal Town together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a good chance for them\Nto understand each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And maybe they'd reach a point where it\Nwouldn't be as awkward in class anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You like the same things.\NYou should be able to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say the same exact thing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Finished the Mega Ogre Omelet Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,And time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:00.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't think you've won just yet, Futaba Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"\NI'll remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stuffed Hut"\NThanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you get along with {\i1}him {\i0}even\Nthough you have similar interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's start a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You took way too long to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the autumn of the arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss Yoko. You should join our band!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, Kondo! You look like\Nyou want to be in a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ River of Three Crossings ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I cannot cross, but still...  ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,--My, what a wonderful voice.\N--♪ The tears trail down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:07.81,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I disappear with the foam, om ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh, I feel dizzy.\N--♪ Om, om, om. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,--She's {\i1}slightly {\i0}out of tune.\N--♪ Om, om, om. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ River of Three Crossings in the beautiful spring ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to pick that flower.\NYamaji, be my ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Get it, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ River of Three Crossings that Kou sings ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.97,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Om, om, om ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,G-Good. You're awake, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You scared me, because you suddenly fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Were those flashes of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,And that was "River of Three Crossings"\Nby Kou Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,So grim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,The River of Three Crossings\Nis like the River Styx, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,People tend to start singing\Nwithout thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:13.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Like when you're alone or\Ntrying to calm a baby down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, you always sing songs dedicated\Nto Eternal in your room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you there's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Nishiyama! Nishiyama! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey, cut it out!\N--♪ Nishiyama! Nishiyama! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Nishiyama, yeah! Nishiyama, whoo! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Nishyama, yeah! Nishiyama, go! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:41.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama got super mad yesterday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't say that after what\Nhappened at Animal Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,She is usually with Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It's strange to see her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:10.30,Main,,0,0,0,,She is still alone. Did she get into a fight\Nwith Nishiyama because of yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,She is all alone, even though she\Nis always usually with her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, bread is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Rice is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if Kondo joins us for lunch today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,When I saw her alone, I couldn't\Nhelp but invite her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not worry over that {\i1}nobody {\i0}who\Ngets mad over such trivial matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko is being excessively welcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,She understands what it's like to be a loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Nishiyama's not a nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.68,Main,,0,0,0,,She's actually really\Nhardworking and a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,She's just intolerant of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's eat lunch. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. So you've known Nishiyama\Nsince elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup. We were in the same group\Nduring a field trip in third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,She was our group leader, and she helped\Nme out when I was a little slow on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,And she's liked roles that end\Nwith "leader" ever since?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:22.63,Main,,0,0,0,,And she wasn't always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You know how things don't always\Ngo the way you want in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,There's someone who's always in her way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:32.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no, is it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama could get along so nicely\Nwith Hayama if she weren't so crotchety.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,They like the same things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,If she were reasonably nice\Non the outside like Hayama,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:48.82,Main,,0,0,0,,she could be the next class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh? Hey--\N--Same goes for you, Nishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:58.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop being so prickly and snobby\Nand talk to people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You're pretty, so I'm sure there\Nare people who admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yeah! When pretty girls aren't friendly,\N--I can't tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,--people won't want to approach them.\N--...if she's complimenting, belittling, or just plain insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,So why not try harder to talk to people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You beat my brother in a\Nchallenge again, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean for it to be a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:44.12,Main,,0,0,0,,And you're always eating lunch with\NNishikawa, always just the three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:51.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Special?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She's so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You're up there with her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,At ramen, you've just got to get veggies\Npiled high, dumplings, and a pork rice bowl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, will you come with me somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see. You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:29.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's friend who has no tact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo is here to buy a cake Nishiyama\Nlikes so they can make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Something that Nishiyama likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Nishiyama's uniform\Nfrom when she worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I said {\i1}cake{\i0}, did I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.24,Main,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're amused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, auntie, you used to be one\Nof Nishikawa's servants, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So Nishikawa really was a rich girl.\NShe can be intimidating and overbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo is pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.35,Main,,0,0,0,,She's as scary as a final boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I really do admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,She should be apologizing after getting\Nmad about something so small,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,but you bought an apology gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:43.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, Miss Yoko. I think you misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:44.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo wasn't alone today because\Nshe got into a fight with Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama was absent, because she was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! I-I just thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,See? I sent a ton of emails to her to see how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:06.81,Main,,0,0,0,,"To: Selina Nishiyama" "How are you feeling? Get better~!"\NSee? I sent a ton of emails to her to see how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! A-All this time I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It was kind of your fault, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,"Asako Kondo"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,"Asako Kondo"\NWhat? She suddenly stopped emailing me after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What? She suddenly stopped emailing me after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,She sent so many in the morning,\NI couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You're so nice, El.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ "E" in "Eternal" is for your\Ncuteness that can't be expressed. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,--She's actually singing a song dedicated to Eternal.\N--♪ "T" is for your tremendous overflowing love. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--So there really is such a song.\N--♪ "T" is for your tremendous overflowing love. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--So there really is such a song.\N--♪ "R" is for reaching beyond hyperspace. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--When should we enter?\N--♪ "R" is for reaching beyond hyperspace. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:09.54,Main,,0,0,0,,--Let's listen until the end. It's such a nice song.\N--♪ "N" is for the nameless blooming flower. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--♪ "N" is for the nameless blooming flower. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,--♪ "N" is for the nameless blooming flower. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ "L" is for...  ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Shino Sonobe.\NI'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life\Nis so entertaini-- I mean, wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:35.56,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."\NRock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm pitch black inside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I can't live in luxury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if there's lots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With three of us, we can eat it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clever and smart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm living resolutely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a full tummy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I spend my days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What makes me smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Food!"{\i0}
